00:33:55.330 --> 00:33:56.330
withstood that.

00:33:56.330 --> 00:34:03.360
So I, I, I think if I had kids I would really
seriously limit their game playing time. I

00:34:03.360 --> 00:34:08.319
just can't imagine it's good for them, which
