00:34:08.319 --> 00:34:13.599
I just think that they should be part of a
healthy, balanced cultural lifestyle, and

00:34:13.599 --> 00:34:16.480
a part of a balanced entertainment intake.

00:34:16.480 --> 00:34:25.640
I also wouldn't let kids play super violent
games until it was the appropriate time for

00:34:25.640 --> 00:34:26.721
them to play them. And the fact that that
is even controversial at all seems kind of

00:34:26.721 --> 00:34:33.230
nuts to me. People say that games don't make
kids violent -- that's probably true. But

00:34:33.230 --> 00:34:39.669
I just think mowing down hundreds of people
every day for hours.

00:34:39.669 --> 00:34:41.560
I-[CHUCKLES]-I-I, maybe it doesn't turn them
