00:47:18.069 --> 00:47:19.069
by one.

00:47:19.069 --> 00:47:25.730
And-and so there is this level of ambiguity
and questioning about what-and it does this

00:47:25.730 --> 00:47:29.690
with very little dialogue, very little explicit
story telling. All the story-storytelling

00:47:29.690 --> 00:47:34.170
