combination of like the-the visual presentation

00:47:34.170 --> 00:47:39.430
of the game and what you're projecting onto
it emotionally. And it's this unbelievably,

00:47:39.430 --> 00:47:41.140
haunting, weird experience.

00:47:41.140 --> 00:47:49.760
That at the end of the game, I was-I was kind
